==Documentation==
A link to a VRC source, such as Creator Docs or API docs.

===Usage===
<code><nowiki>{{</nowiki>VRC link|<nowiki>https://vrchat.com</nowiki>|VRChat Home page<nowiki>}}</nowiki></code> will be turned into {{VRC link|https://vrchat.com|VRChat Home page}}.

Note: Do not use this template for links to the [https://vrchatapi.github.io/ VRChat API Documentation].

